{"key":"processedPost-17203602","value":{"id":17203602,"first":17203206,"last":17204586,"when":1352691692,"utime":"11/12/12 05:41 AM","content":"It's hard to get a lot of mycology supplies at regular stores because the demand is too low for them to stock the stuff.&nbsp; You can get agar-agar at health and asian food markets.&nbsp; You can get malt extract at health food or beer brewing shops. Blend the agar-agar into a flour with a coffee grinder and then boil to mix and dissolve the agar and malt.&nbsp; Pour into a flask and sterilize as shown in the <a href=\"http://www.mushroomvideos.com/Agar-Petri-Dishes\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\">agar/petri dishes video</a>.<br />RR","title":"Re: Best nationwide stores to purchase agar in the USA?","forum":"Mushroom Cultivation"}}